movie2= Movie.create(title:"300", description:"Based on Frank Miller's graphic novel, '300' is very loosely based the 480 B.C. Battle of Thermopylae, where the King of Sparta led his army against the advancing Persians; the battle is said to have inspired all of Greece to band together against the Persians, and helped usher in the world's first democracy.",
